Content: if 1 chain can do 100 tx/sec, 10,000 independent chains can do 1 million tx/sec. this is not so hard to believe

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: the key is that using the notarized burn protocol, we can ensure the total coin supply across all chains stays constant, ie. they are fungible. it is sharding upside down. we combine independent chains at least enough to be able to prove any given txid was confirmed
